This archive contains one 320k (8-sector double sided) disk image in Transcopy, TeleDisk, Copy II PC, and ImageDisk format. These images will recreate the original copy protected disk. See the Unprotect folder for a patch. SuperCard Pro and Kryoflux images have also been added. 

