Windows Neptune is slow to load after logon due to a misbehaving service.', 'Build 5111 is the only leaked build which was titled the *Microsoft Neptune Developer Release* and has a version number of 5.5.5111 (which Windows XP and 2003, 5.1 and 5.2 respectively will see as a newer version).

