Repair and optimize OS X Beta disks while booted under OS 9,
Rebuild Directories with Volume Recover,
Rebuild desktop from scratch by deleting it with Norton Disk Doctor,
Add a single file to the Desktop database,
Repair and optimize, wipe free space and recover files from the Contextual Menus,
Define how Speed Disk arrange files with Speed Disk Profiles.
', 'MacOS', null);
